(9108, 1, '2016-02-16 11:48:14', '2016-02-16 11:48:14', '[vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="7/12"][distance type="4"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><strong>Conversion Rate Optimization</strong></h1>\nIn internet marketing, conversion optimization, or conversion rate optimization (CRO) is a system for increasing the percentage of visitors to a website that convert into customers, or more generally, take any desired action on a webpage.\nConversion rate optimization (CRO) is the process of optimizing your sponsored search ads, landing pages, and overall website design to raise your conversion rate.\nCRO is quickly gaining in popularity because it''s seen as a way to increase profits from sales without raising your advertising spends.\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][distance type="2"][vc_single_image image="9109" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="2"][maxtitle type="5" maxtitle_content="What is a <strong>Conversion?</strong>"][vc_column_text]\n<p class="aligncenter slog-tx3" style="max-width: 580px;">A conversion is the specific action you want your web visitor to take on your website or landing page, such as:</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][iconbox type="7" icon_title="Purchasing" icon_name="li_banknote"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="7" icon_title="A button or link click" icon_name="sl-mouse"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][iconbox type="7" icon_title="Registration" icon_name="sl-user-follow"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="7" icon_title="Downloading brochure" icon_name="sl-cloud-download"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][iconbox type="7" icon_title="Refer a friend" icon_name="sl-present"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="7" icon_title="Reaching a particular page" icon_name="sl-layers"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9510" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>What is Conversion Rate Optimization?</strong></h4>\nConversion Rate optimization is an art of generating more and more leads from the targeted audience. Conversion optimization makes your customers pick up the phone and call for a quote. Conversion optimization gets them to click the ‘buy’ button now instead of leaving the tab open for later.\nBy optimizing or improving your web conversion rate you can get more people to take more action without spending money on attracting more visits to your landing page or website.\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_bgcolor="#f6f8f9"][vc_column][distance type="4"][maxtitle type="5" maxtitle_content="How <strong>We Do</strong>"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="1"][vc_column][buy_process process_item="%5B%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22Website%20%3Cstrong%3EUsability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%22%2C%22process_content%22%3A%22Increase%20your%20customer%20base%20and%20online%20conversion%20rate%20with%20our%20website%20usability%20services%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-cubes%22%2C%22line_flag%22%3A%221%22%2C%22process_style%22%3A%22default%22%7D%2C%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22Improve%20%3Cstrong%3Esales%20copy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%22%2C%22process_content%22%3A%22We%20can%20craft%20compelling%20sales%20copy%20for%20your%20website%20that%20will%20encourage%20your%20site%20visitors%20to%20convert%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-cog%22%2C%22line_flag%22%3A%222%22%2C%22process_style%22%3A%22default%22%7D%2C%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22conversion%20%3Cstrong%3Efunnel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%22%2C%22process_content%22%3A%22We%20can%20analyze%20your%20conversion%20funnel%20and%20make%20improvements%20to%20increase%20conversion%20rate%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-filter%22%2C%22line_flag%22%3A%223%22%2C%22process_style%22%3A%22featured%22%7D%2C%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22Home%20%3Cstrong%3EOptimization%3C%2Fstrong%3E%22%2C%22process_content%22%3A%22Our%20Landing%20Page%20Optimization%20services%20allow%20us%20to%20optimize%20your%20site%20for%20better%20conversion%20rates%5Cn%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-home%22%2C%22line_flag%22%3A%224%22%2C%22process_style%22%3A%22default%22%7D%2C%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22A%2FB%20%3Cstrong%3ESplit%20Testing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%22%2C%22process_content%22%3A%22We%20provide%20AB%20testing%20experiments%20targeting%20the%20pages%20that%20will%20give%20you%20the%20biggest%20uplift%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-random%22%2C%22line_flag%22%3A%225%22%2C%22process_style%22%3A%22default%22%7D%5D"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong>Our Approach </strong></h4>\n<ul class="arrow">\n 	<li>First, we get to know your business and your goals, so we can determine what the best strategy will be for creating or optimizing your Conversion Rate Optimization.</li>\n 	<li>As a conversion rate optimization company, our data-driven A/B tests and further UX improvements look to continuously improve your conversion rates, grow your contacts database, and drive more revenue.</li>\n 	<li>We analyze the results from our experiments to understand whether our hypothesis was correct. If a statistical significance has been reached and our hypothesis is correct, we roll out the successful variation of your landing page. If not, we test a new hypothesis and run the whole process again.</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance][vc_single_image image="9465" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_im