(9471, 1, '2016-04-07 08:12:12', '2016-04-07 08:12:12', '[vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="7/12"][distance type="4"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><strong>Ecommerce Marketing</strong></h1>\nE-commerce marketing is the practice of guiding online shoppers to an e-commerce website and persuading them to buy the products or services online. A successful e-commerce marketing team needs to have expertise in search engine optimization, pay-per-click marketing, social media marketing, and display advertising to reach the top of search results.[/vc_column_text][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][distance][vc_single_image image="9472" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="2"][maxtitle type="5" heading="1" maxtitle_content="Our <strong>Services</strong>"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="19" icon_title="Search Engine Optimization" iconbox_content="We can help supercharge your SEO initiatives and plan or execute ecommerce SEO campaigns that deliver high ROI." icon_link_text="LEARN MORE" icon_link_url="http://webnus.biz/themes/easyweb/seo/search-engine-optimization/" icon_name="sl-globe-alt"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="19" icon_title="Pay Per Click Management" iconbox_content="Bring qualified, targeted shoppers to your ecommerce store with a custom PPC strategy built specifically for your store." icon_link_text="LEARN MORE" icon_link_url="http://webnus.biz/themes/easyweb/seo/pay-per-click/" icon_name="sl-mouse"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="19" icon_title="Social Media Optimization" iconbox_content="Our social media optimization services include various large social media networks like Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Google+ etc. " icon_link_text="LEARN MORE" icon_link_url="http://webnus.biz/themes/easyweb/seo/social-media-marketing/" icon_name="sl-share"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Search engine optimization</h3>\n<strong>Search engine optimization</strong>, better known as SEO, is one of the most critical parts of e-commerce marketing. It is based on special algorithms that analyze the instances of specific keywords on your website. Because users navigate the Internet through search engines like Google, these results play a large role in the success of your website. A good SEO campaign can position your e-commerce website to rise to the top of the Google rankings.[/vc_column_text][button btn_content="UNDERSTAND MORE" url="http://webnus.biz/themes/easyweb/seo/search-engine-optimization/"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="8964" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="5/12"][distance][vc_single_image image="9082" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Pay-per-click</h3>\n<strong>Pay-per-click</strong> advertising operates similarly to SEO since it is based on keywords. However, whereas search engine optimization works organically (meaning that a marketing firm doesn’t have to pay for it), PPC results are the results that show up in yellow boxes on Google.[/vc_column_text][button btn_content="UNDERSTAND MORE" url="http://webnus.biz/themes/easyweb/seo/pay-per-click/"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/12"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="2"][distance type="4"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Social media marketing</h3>\n<p class="pad-r40"><strong>Social media marketing</strong> can be very important to e-commerce websites. By creating an effective Facebook business page and enticing potential customers to ‘like’ your page with exclusive offers and discounts, you will not only gain immeasurable word-of-mouth advertising through the network, but will establish yourself as a trustworthy, reputable Internet business.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][button btn_content="UNDERSTAND MORE" url="http://webnus.biz/themes/easyweb/seo/social-media-marketing/"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9072" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="6/12"][vc_single_image image="9478" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="4/12"][distance type="5"][distance type="4"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Display advertising</h3>\n<strong>Display advertising</strong> can be intimidating to smaller Internet retailers, but it has been found to be very worthwhile. By buying small banner ads on related blogs, message boards and other websites, you can showcase your business in front of people who wouldn’t have found it otherwise.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/12"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][line][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row blox_class="cntborder"][vc_column width="5/12" css=".vc_custom_1448871957642{background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;}"][distance][webnus-divider type="7" lspan="What" rspan="Clients Say" color="#77da55"][distance][vc_column_text]We do not only provide SEO and Internet marketing services but we also offer a wide array of related services such as SEO friendly web design, pay per click, affiliate marketing, website audits, social media optimization, branding and several others.[/vc_column_text][distance][testimonial_slider type="penta"][testimonial_item name="John Anderson" img="8876" subtitle="Risotto Co" testimonial_content="One of the best theme I have ever used. 