(11407, 1, '2016-11-09 10:17:57', '2016-11-09 10:17:57', '[vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="7/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><strong>Affiliate Marketing</strong></h1>\nAffiliate marketing is the process of earning a commission by promoting other people''s (or company''s) products. You find a product you like, promote it to others, and earn a piece of the profit for each sale that you make. Affiliate marketing is a cost effective means of combining established marketing techniques with technology for business success.[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="9102" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9527" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][distance][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>How Does Affiliate Marketing Work?</strong></h4>\nAffiliate marketing is generally defined as a referral program that gives commissions those who successfully refer a potential client or leads to your site. Sometimes called an advertising affiliate Internet program, it is one of the most cost-effective and efficient means to drive online revenue.\n\nThe more people who are advertising your company, services, or products online, the more successful you will be. An affiliate marketing is essentially a sales force compensated based on their performance. Creating an affiliate marketing program will allow you to focus your attention on other aspects of your business.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="2"][maxtitle type="5" heading="1" maxtitle_content="Our <strong>Values</strong>"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="10" icon_title="Effective strategies" iconbox_content="An individual map is created according to the customized needs of the clients for achieving scalable results." icon_name="sl-bulb"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="10" icon_title="Branding Transparency" iconbox_content="Our brand network is 100% transparent - you will always know where and when your ads are showing." icon_name="sl-trophy"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="10" icon_title="Proactive Management" iconbox_content="We’ll help recruit new affiliates and communicate with existing ones to ensure results are maximized." icon_name="sl-layers"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="10" icon_title="Cost Effectiveness" iconbox_content="Our goal is to provide Affiliate Marketing services, which maximize your ROI and keep your costs down." icon_name="li_banknote"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][line][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="4"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>What we do</strong></h4>\n<ul class="check">\n	<li>Help select the right affiliate networks that meet your goals</li>\n	<li>Set up the affiliate program on the chosen networks</li>\n	<li>Promote your affiliate program; review the affiliate application &amp; signup new affiliates</li>\n	<li>Create marketing collaterals for affiliates - images, banners &amp; catalogs</li>\n	<li>Monthly, weekly &amp; ad hoc affiliate communication</li>\n	<li>Set up data feeds for affiliates</li>\n	<li>Analyze individual affiliate''s performance and communicate with them to help them</li>\n	<li>Periodic reports on the performance of the affiliate marketing channel</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9524" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_image="9540" blox_padding_bottom="40" blox_dark="true" blox_bgcolor="#77da55"][vc_column width="1/6"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][distance type="5"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text css_animation="appear"]\n<h4 style="text-align: center; font-size: 44px;"><strong>Why choose us?</strong></h4>\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">Our agency-level relationships span over all major affiliate networks, including Commission Junction, Impact Radius, eBay Enterprise, CAKE and LinkShare. These relationships help to ensure that the best rates are negotiated for our clients. Excellent rates, combined with our methodical approach to the Affiliate selection process, enables Rise Interactive to partner with publishers that embrace our client''s brands, drive conversions and achieve ROI goals.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row blox_class="cntborder"][vc_column width="5/12" css=".vc_custom_1448871957642{background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;}"][distance][webnus-divider type="7" lspan="What" rspan="Clients Say" color="#77da55"][distance][vc_column_text]We do not only provide SEO and Internet marketing services but we also offer a wide array of related services such as SEO friendly web design, pay per click, affiliate marketing, website audits, social media optimization, branding and several others.[/vc_column_text][distance][testimonial_slider type="penta"][testimonial_item name="John Anderson" img="8876" subtitle="Risotto Co" testimonial_content="One of the best theme I have ever used. Every minor detail has been taken care of. Clean, Modern Design can be used for any type of website. Excellent template." second_social="instagram"][testimonial_item name="Lida Smith" img="8880" subtitle="Mexin Co" testimonial_content="Lida has assisted me with questions in regards to web hosting and has offered me more insight in half an hour than my current host did in all the years I have been with them." first_social="instagram" second_social="linkedin" third_social="vimeo" fourth_social="pinterest"][/testimonial_slider][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/12" css=".vc_custom_1448868540278{background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12"][distance][webnus-divider type="7" lspan="Request" rspan="A Free Quote" color="#77da55"][distance][contact-form-7 id="31"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_padding_top="40" blox_padding_bottom="40" blox_bgcolor="#f9f9f9"][vc_column][distance type="2"][portfolio-carousel title="CASE STUDIES"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Affiliate Marketing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9101-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-09 10:17:57', '2016-11-09 10:17:57', '', 9101, 'http://localhost/Destinations/2016/11/09/9101-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
