(11414, 1, '2016-11-09 10:17:59', '2016-11-09 10:17:59', '[vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="7/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><strong>Content Marketing</strong></h1>\nWhat is content exactly? Content is blogs, infographics, videos, emails, eBooks, social media updates, and the text on your website. Yep, content is everywhere. Which is why it’s so important to have a content marketing strategy that aligns your content with your core values and each of your audiences’ wants, needs, and unique, preferred ways of consuming content.[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][distance type="2"][vc_single_image image="9090" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance][vc_single_image image="9525" img_size="full"][distance type="3"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][distance type="5"][distance type="4"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Why Do You Need Content Marketing?</h3>\nBuyers are self-directed and content can help satisfy their quest for answers and enable you to direct them to solutions for their business problems. The team at EasySeo Marketing is experts in helping businesses like yours determine how to take your audience from prospects to buyers.[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>How Can Content Marketing Help You Get More Customers?</h3>\nContent marketing creates signals across the web that builds credibility and authority with your audience. In addition to the many SEO benefits of content marketing, it can be used as a means to connect on a level with your customers that other digital marketing can’t.[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_imag