(11421, 1, '2016-11-09 10:18:02', '2016-11-09 10:18:02', '[vc_row row_type="1"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias="creative-freedom"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_bgcolor="#f6f6f5"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h1 class="respo-tagline" style="text-align: center;">How to Get your Business <strong> <span style="color: #4ff37c;">Online</span></strong></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][distance][vc_column_text]\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 17px; color: #444; margin-bottom: 23px;">You can create your company’s online presence in several ways. Explore all your options for\ngetting your business online and see what works best for you.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][distance type="5"][vc_tta_tabs style="modern" shape="round" color="white" spacing="35" gap="35" alignment="center" active_section="1" no_fill_content_area="true"][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-dot-circle-o" tab_id="1453793687346-39827114-1e6a" add_icon="true"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style="text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 25px;">CHOOSE YOUR <span style="color: #4ff37c;">DOMAIN</span></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9809" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="left-to-right"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]If you’re thinking of starting up online, or creating a new blog, finding a memorable name can be a great way of boosting your chances of success. But, choosing one can be really tricky. It’s one of the most difficult steps in getting started.\n\nThere are a lot of things to consider and it can feel overwhelming, so here are some tips to make it easier. After all, your website is the face of your business online. We’ll cover the following topics:[/vc_column_text][distance][vc_column_text][one_half][list-ul type="check"][li-row]Make it memorable[/li-row][li-row]Make it short[/li-row][li-row]Make it easy to spell[/li-row][/list-ul][/one_half][one_half][list-ul type="check"][li-row]Avoid hyphens [/li-row][li-row]Avoid trademarked names[/li-row][li-row]Include relevant keywords[/li-row][/list-ul]\n[/one_half][/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]All of the factors we’ve discussed should be considered when choosing your domain name.  Based on your situation you may disregard some to focus on others, and that’s fine.  These factors will help you make the best choice for your business from the available options.[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_type="linecons" i_icon_linecons="vc_li vc_li-data" tab_id="1454228797284-23ab691b-78a1" add_icon="true"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style="text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 25px;">CHOOSE YOUR <span style="color: #4ff37c;">HOST</span></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9810" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="left-to-right"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Determining Your Needs </strong></h6>\nLook at your current website. When choosing a web host, always try to keep the future in mind and plan accordingly.\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Choose hosting Type</strong></h6>\nThere are three general types of servers offered by web hosting companies: Shared, virtual and dedicated servers.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Comparing Features</strong></h6>\nCompare important feature such as storage, bandwidth, acceptable security tools and server operating system\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Order web Hosting</strong></h6>\nSelect the web hosting package. After the order is processed, you receive an e-mail that contains further instructions about your account[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_type="linecons" i_icon_linecons="vc_li vc_li-pen" tab_id="1454228839423-c53893db-b78e" add_icon="true"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style="text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 25px;">WEBSITE <span style="color: #4ff37c;">DESIGN</span></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9811" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="left-to-right"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Planning</strong></h6>\nThe planning stage is arguably the most important, because what’s decided and mapped here sets the stage for the entire project.\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Design</strong></h6>\nThe design stage typically involves moving the information outlined in the planning stage further into reality. The main deliverable is a visual representation.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Development</strong></h6>\nDevelopment involves the bulk of the programming work, as well as loading content (whether by your team or the client’s).\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Launch</strong></h6>\nThe purpose of the launch phase is to prepare the website for public viewing. This requires final polishing of design elements and most of all, a consideration of the user experience.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_type="linecons" i_icon_linecons="vc_li vc_li-search" tab_id="1454228834892-9f894ebc-dfde" add_icon="true"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style="text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 25px;">SEARCH ENGINE<span style="color: #4ff37c;"> OPTIMIZATION</span></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9812" img_size="full" alignment="center" css_animation="left-to-right"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Keyword Analysis</strong></h6>\nWe research your industry to determine which terms are most often used to find businesses like yours.\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> On-Page SEO</strong></h6>\nOptimizing your content for search includes tasks like keyword usage, keyword placement, readability and more[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Link Building</strong></h6>\nOur expert Link Builders are focused on building authoritative and relevant links to your site.\n<h6>[icon name="fa-check" size="16px" color="#00c2e5"] <strong> Local SEO services</strong></h6>\nOur local SEO services provide everything you need to rank and drive traffic in your local market. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row blox_class="border-btm"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h1 class="respo-tagline" style="text-align: center;">Why Choose<strong> <span style="color: #4ff37c;">US</span></strong></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][iconbox type="8" icon_title="<strong>Integrated</strong> services" iconbox_content="As a leading digital agency we