(11431, 1, '2016-11-09 10:18:19', '2016-11-09 10:18:19', '[vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="7/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><strong>Pay Per Click</strong></h1>\n<strong>PPC</strong> stands for pay-per-click, a model of internet marketing in which advertisers pay a fee each time one of their ads is clicked. Essentially, it’s a way of buying visits to your site, rather than attempting to “earn” those visits organically.\nSearch engine advertising is one of the most popular forms of PPC. It allows advertisers to bid for ad placement in a search engine''s sponsored links when someone searches on a keyword that is related to their business offering.\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="9082" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>PPC Management</strong></h4>\nPlatforms such as Google AdWords and Bing Ads are important to your business. With our pay-per-click marketing (PPC) expertise, we can help take your accounts to the next level. We customize strategy and reporting tailored to your needs.\nWe provide the support and guidance you require to accomplish your goal, be it maximizing return on investment, increasing leads, or driving brand awareness.[/vc_column_text][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9448" img_size="full"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_padding_top="70" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column][maxtitle type="5" maxtitle_content="Our Pay Per Click <strong>Services</strong>"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_padding_top="1" blox_padding_bottom="15" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="3"][iconbox icon_title="PPC Audits" iconbox_content="Our PPC Audit process starts from understanding audit objective, coverage and leading to data analysis.\n\n" icon_name="sl-eyeglass"][distance type="2"][iconbox icon_title="Bing Advertising" iconbox_content="Our in-house Bing ads agency team has the training and expertise you need to make the most of Bing’s popular PPC platform.\n" icon_name="fa-windows"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="3"][iconbox icon_title="Social Advertising" iconbox_content="EasySeo can help you with paid social campaigns that can drive your target audience toward much targeted desired actions.\n\n" icon_name="sl-rocket"][distance type="2"][iconbox icon_title="Display Advertising" iconbox_content="Your display ads will be targeting an audience that has already indicated an interest in your service or product.\n\n" icon_name="fa-bullhorn"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="3"][iconbox icon_title="Google AdWords" iconbox_content=" Hiring us gives you the benefit of a full-time AdWords expert without the extra cost of hiring another full-time employee." icon_name="fa-google"][distance type="2"][iconbox icon_title="Remarketing &amp; Retargeting" iconbox_content="Improve ROI and increase conversions by marketing to people who have all ready visited your website.\n\n" icon_name="sl-refresh"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="4"][vc_single_image image="9450" img_size="full"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]\n<h4><strong>Brief process of our pay per click campaign:</strong></h4>\nOur pay-per-click (PPC) management service includes the following components:\n<ul class="check">\n	<li>PPC search campaign strategy</li>\n	<li>Keyword research and selection</li>\n	<li>Ad creative development</li>\n	<li>Campaign set-up</li>\n	<li>Bid management and ROI tracking</li>\n	<li>Landing page optimization and development</li>\n	<li>Campaign management and analysis</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_image="9535" blox_padding_top="15" blox_padding_bottom="10" blox_dark="true" blox_bgcolor="#77da55"][vc_column][distance type="3"][distance type="3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text css_animation="appear"]\n<h4 style="text-align: center; font-size: 44px;"><strong>Deliverables</strong></h4>\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">We report monthly on your campaign’s success regarding keyword choice and text choice, and we create a rank report so you know where you rank organically for the keywords you pay for. Additionally, after you review the report, we’ll book a one hour call with the members of your team to explain your campaign’s progress, direction, and answer any questions you may have.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][distance type="2"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row blox_class="cntborder"][vc_column width="5/12" css=".vc_custom_1448871957642{background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;}"][distance][webnus-divider type="7" lspan="What" rspan="Clients Say" color="#77da55"][distance][vc_column_text]We do not only provide SEO and Internet marketing services but we also offer a wide array of related services such as SEO friendly web design, pay per click, affiliate marketing, website audits, social media optimization, branding and several others.[/vc_column_text][distance][testimonial_slider type="penta"][testimonial_item name="John Anderson" img="8876" subtitle="Risotto Co" testimonial_content="One of the best theme I have ever used. Every minor detail has been taken care of. Clean, Modern Design can be used for any type of website. Excellent template." second_social="instagram"][testimo