wn for some excitement. You can do Karting at Kanakpura Main road and climbing at Residency road.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-163" src="https://indiator.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/rock-climbing.jpg" alt="rock-climbing" width="763" height="453" />\r\n\r\n<strong>See the powerful stage show</strong> – Spending time in the movie hall, go to watch the live<strong> stage show at Ranga Shankara</strong>. It’s an iconic stage, which gives chance to not only the well-known performers, but also to the newcomers too.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-164" src="https://indiator.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ranga-shankara.jpg" alt="ranga-shankara" width="785" height="483" />\r\n\r\nAmong all these splendid things to do, Bangalore has some more activities and places to visit. So, it’s better to plan and book a <a href="https://indiator.com"><strong>Bangalore tour package</strong> </a>rather than to read it on the internet and take a virtual glimpses of the natural and ancient sights of Bangalore.', 'Top Things to do in Bangalore, India', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11510-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-09 11:55:33', '2016-11-09 11:55:33', '', 11510, 'http://localhost/Destinations/2016/11/09/11510-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
